ow"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-26_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-27_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-29_">How Do I Contact Bar &amp; Cocoa?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-30_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-32_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Questions?&nbsp;</span>We're here to help!</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We're available 9am to 5pm Monday through Friday.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">You can send us an using the message bubble on the bottom right corner.</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Someone will reply to you same day during work hours, or next business day when you send a message after hours.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-33_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-34_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-36_">Is The Packaging Recyclable?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-37_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-39_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We make every effort to use eco-friendly and minimal packaging to ship each order, while protecting bars/products from breaking/melting.<br><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">BOX and PAPER LINERS (Sealed Air)&nbsp;</span>- these are curbside recyclable</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">BIODEGRADABLE ICE -&nbsp;</span>these will biodegrade in landfills and can be thrown in the trash.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">ENVIRO ICE -&nbsp;</span>Discard the gel in the sink, it's drain safe and non-toxic. Or use it as plant food. And recycle the #4 plastic bag.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">FOIL LINERS&nbsp;</span>- these are not not recyclable and go out with trash</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-40_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-41_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-43_">How Do I Find Ingredient/Allergen Information?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-44_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-46_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">On each product page we have helpful icons to tell you about the ingredients/allergens.<br><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">These DIET icons can have one slash in the circle or an X on the cirlce. One slash indicates traces of, or use of shared equipment. (Such as traces of tree nuts.) An X on the icon means it is completely free of that allergen.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">When in doubt, please send us a message before ordering and we'll check the ingredients for you.</p></span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-47_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-48_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-49_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-51_">How Do You Source Your Products?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-52_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-54_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">The makers we feature source their cacao through direct trade. Therefore, local cacao farmers are paid better and makers can nurture higher standards for premium quality cacao and sustainable agroforestry.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">All of the chocolate and confections we carry are free of child or slave labor practices.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-55_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-56_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-58_">How Do You Source Your Products?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-59_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-61_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">You are automatically enrolled in our Rewards program when you create an account. Points will be honored for your all orders placed with the same email address.</span><br></p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-62_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-63_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-65_">How Do I Work With Bar &amp; Cocoa?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-66_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-68_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">For all inquiries related to partnerships/promotions please use the chat bubble to send a message.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">If you're a bean to bar chocolate maker and you'd like to be considered for our club or store, we may ask for samples to see if you're a fit. While we're open, please understand that we get many requests, and that sending samples does not guarantee feedback or that we will feature your bars.</p></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-jIkYaL eUPoJu pf-69_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-70_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-72_">Shipping &amp; Returns</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-73_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-75_">Questions about shipping? We can help.</span></p><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-76_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-77_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-78_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-80_">When Does My Order Ship?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-81_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-83_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Store Purchases</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Orders ship on business days Monday thru Thursday to prevent melt. We monitor weather and transit time to determine when we can ship, to ensure the chocolate arrives to you safely. If temperatures are too hot we reserve the right to hold your order until it is cooler.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Club Subscribers</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Bar &amp; Cocoa subscriptions ship out immediately for the first month, and then early in the second week of every month for all subsequent deliveries as long as they are at least a week apart.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Examples&nbsp;</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Subscription ordered:&nbsp;February 15th - First box shipped by Feb 17th. Second box ships March 10th</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Subscription ordered:&nbsp;February 27th - First box shipped by Feb 28th. Second box ships April 9th.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-84_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-85_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-87_">How Do You Package &amp; Ship The Chocolate</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-88_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-90_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We utilize&nbsp;minimal eco-friendly packaging to ship each order. In the warmer months, we add ice and insulation to ensure your chocolate arrives in perfect condition. Our ice packs are 100% biodegradable. It helps if you keep an eye out on delivery days and bring in your package as soon as possible.&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">We reserve the right to hold your order if temperature is above 100F.</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We use USPS or Fedex Ground for most standard day shipments and Fedex Express for priority 2 Day shipments for continental US orders. We ship anywhere almost anywhere in the world and shipping for international orders is calculated at checkout.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Bar &amp; Cocoa is not responsible for delays resulting from mishandling by the shipping carrier.&nbsp;We reserve the right to change shipping methods at any time without notice.</span></p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-91_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-92_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-94_">What About International Shipping?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-97_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We love sending chocolate all around the world. Because of the costs associated with shipping internationally,&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">all&nbsp;international orders are final sale.</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Please review your country's international custom and duties as we are not responsible for the payment of those fees.<span style="font-weight: bolder;">&nbsp;The club subscription is only available in the United States at this time.</span></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">We ship to over 80 countries usually via DHL Express or Fedex. Shipping cost is dynamic, and calculated at checkout based on the total weight.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">No shipping options available? We may not be able to ship to your country due to customs restrictions.</p></span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-98_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-99_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-100_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-102_">How Can I Track My Order?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-103_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-105_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">Tracking numbers are emailed to you upon shipment. When in doubt, check your email or your store account. If you can't find it, we can resend it to you. Send us a message using the chat bubble on the bottom right corner.</span><br></p></span></p><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-106_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-108_">My Order is Damaged, Lost, or Melted</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-109_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-111_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">Please message us with your order number using the chat below and we'll make it right. We'll track it down and take care of it for you.</span><br></p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-112_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-113_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-115_">Refunds</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-116_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-118_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">While we make every effort to ensure your chocolate arrives in perfect condition, mailing chocolate in warm weather comes with risk.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">If your order contains bloomed or melted chocolate, send us a message with a picture of the bars to<span style="font-weight: bolder;">&nbsp;within 24 hours of arrival</span>. We will either refund your order, or replace your chocolate (depending on stock), or in the case of a subscription, add a free month.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-119_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-120_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-122_">Returns</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-123_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-125_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Unfortunately, we do not accept returns. Chocolates are not refundable since they are a food item. However if you are unhappy for any reason, please message us within 7 days of receipt of your order or call (877) 778-8599 and we'll do what we can to make it right.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">If we haven't answered your questions on this page reach out anytime. We're here to help!</p></span></p></div></div></div></div><div data-pf-expandable="true" style="display:none" data-pf-type="TabsContent" class="sc-jIkYaL eUPoJu pf-126_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-127_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-129_">Subscription Club FAQ</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-132_">Questions about our club? We can help.</span></p><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-133_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-134_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-135_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-137_">What Does My Chocolate Subscription Include?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-138_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-140_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">Bar &amp; Cocoa chocolate club&nbsp;include 4 bars of bean to bar chocolate every month. We ship the bars we love (and we hope you do, too!) Your&nbsp;chocolate subscription box will arrive once every month. You can read tasting notes about chocolate bars and makers we feature. Your feedback helps us pick our future chocolate selections!</span><br></p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-141_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-142_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-144_">I'm Buying a Gift, How Do I Tell the Recipient?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-145_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-147_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">For club subscriptions, we do not email the gift recipient beforehand. When you check "This is a Gift" you can add a gift note, which we print on a card and include with their first box.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">For store orders, you can select a gift box option, and put a note that'd you'd like to include during check out.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">You can also print out this&nbsp;<a href="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1120/9400/files/Gift_Certificate.pdf?v=1611419170" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Chocolate Club Gift Certificate</a>&nbsp;to give it to your recipient.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-148_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-149_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-151_">How Does Billing Work?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-152_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-154_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Orders placed in our Store are billed immediately. For subscriptions, you are billed immediately upon checkout. Subscriptions are re-billed on the 20th every 3, 6, 12 months depending on your term.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Subscriptions renew automatically,&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: bolder;">UNLESS specified to be a Gift.&nbsp;</span>You can cancel automatic renewal by logging into your&nbsp;<a href="http://club.barandcocoa.com/customer/login" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"><span style="font-weight: bolder;">Club Account</span></a>. (Club &amp; Store are separate logins and accounts.)</p></span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-155_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-156_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-157_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-159_">How Can I Change or Cancel My Subscription</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-160_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-162_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">Your Bar &amp; Cocoa&nbsp;subscription is&nbsp;automatically renewed&nbsp;for your convenience unless you specify it as a gift during checkout. You can skip a month, change the delivery address, cancel your renewal, or make updates to your subscription at any time by logging in to your&nbsp;</span><a href="http://club.barandcocoa.com/customer/login" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">Club Account</a><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">. If you have issues, contact us on chat.</span><br></p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-163_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-164_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-166_">What If My Chocolate Arrived Melted?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-167_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-169_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Shipments to warmer cities, or anywhere during warm weather months, may include an ice packs and insulation to prevent melt. We take precautions to protect your chocolate. We recommend being available on delivery days (you receive an email when your order ships so you can get it indoors as soon as possible.</p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><br></p><p style="line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;">Please have your chocolate shipped to a location where it is&nbsp;not left outside in the heat&nbsp;whenever possible. In the unlikely event that you experience issues with your order, please contact us immediately, and we'll make it right.</p></span></p></div></div><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:4;--c-lg:4"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-170_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-iJKOzS YwOzI pf-171_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-173_">Can You Ship Subscriptions Internationally?</span></h3><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-174_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-176_"><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.96px; color: rgb(33, 31, 30); font-family: Gotham, sans-serif;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.96px;">At this time Club subscriptions are only available in the United States.</span><br></p></span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-177_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-178_"><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-179_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-181_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">You Didn't Answer My Question!</span></span></p><p class="sc-jeqYYF hzMUYW pf-182_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-ZOsLE HTdit pf-184_">We are happy to speak with you any time! <b>Chat and message us using the&nbsp;orange chat bubble </b>(on the bottom right corner). Messages will be returned within 1-2 business days (although we are usually a lot quicker than that!) We generally work Monday through Fridays from 9am to 5pm.&nbsp;</span></p></div></div></div><div class="sc-bBHHQT iVWrCP pf-185_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-jObXwK cBBNUN pf-186_"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><script>window.__pagefly_setting__={"baseURL":"https://apps.pagefly.io","analyticsURL":"https://analytics.pagefly.io","isBackend":false,"cdnURL":"https://cdn.pagefly.io","pageflyVersion":"3.1.3","shopDomain":"chocorush.myshopify.com","elementData":{},"pageTitle":"Help & Contact Us","pageType":"page","pageId":"7ab64aae-8ffc-42b1-9599-a7c3b73e6a57","lazyLoad":false,"forceByPassGoogleLightHouse":false,"imageLazyLoad":false,"nativeImageLazyLoad":false,"useThemeJQ":false,"fontLink":"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400&display=swap","trackingIDs":[],"shopifyProxyPath":"/a/pf_preview"};window.__pagefly_setting__.moneyFormat={{shop.money_format|json}};</script><script src="https://cdn.pagefly.io/pagefly/3.1.3/core/helper.js" defer></script>